  "texts": [
    "In conclusion, government should guide parents but not tell them how to parent in law.",
    "Parents should be told about the risks and benefits to young children using phones and tablets through public awareness but it should not be made illegal for them to allow their children to use it.",
    "This is a fair way of doing things as there is no clear evidence either way as to what young children using electronic devices will do to them."
  ],
